quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,189,"(Allah) Ndivo vakakusikai kubva kumunhu mumwechete (Adam), uye vakasika kubva kwaari mudzimai wake (Hawwa (Evha)) kuti ave anofara nekugara naye. Paakasangana (murume asingatendi kubva kuvana vaAdam) naye (mukadzi wake asingatendi) pabonde akatakura pamuviri zvisina matambudziko. Uye pakakura pamuviri, vakakumbira Allah, Tenzi vavo (vachiti): “Kana mukatipa akanaka (mwana), zvirokwazvo, tichava avo vevanotenda.”"
  7,190,"Zvino (Allah) pavakavapa (murume nemukadzi wake vasingatendi) mwana akanaka, vakavapa (Allah) vabatsiri mune izvo zvavakanaga vavapa. Asi Allah vari pamusoro peizvo zvavanovasanganisa nazvo sevabatsiri"
  7,191,Varikusanganisa here naAllah avo vasingakwanisi kusika chimwe chinhu asi ivo vakatosikwawo
  7,192,"Hapana rubatsiro rwavanokwanisa kuvapa, kana pachavo kuzvibetsera"
  7,193,"Uye kana mukavasheedzera kuchokwadi, havakuteverei. Zvakafanana kwamuri kuvasheedza kana kunyarara"
  7,194,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vamunosheedza kunze kwaAllah varanda vakafanana nemi. Naizvozvo vasheedzei vagokudairai kana muri pachokwadi"
  7,195,"Vane makumbo here avanofamba nawo? Kana kuti vane maoko here avanobata nawo? Kana kuti vane maziso here avanoona nawo? Kana kuti vane nzeve here dzavanonzwa nadzo? Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Daidzai shamwari dzenyu dzamunosanganisa naAllah uye mondirongera (zvakaipa), uye musandipa nguva!”"
  7,196,"“Zvirokwazvo, muchengeti wangu ndiAllah avo vakadzikisa Bhuku (Qur’aan), uye ndivo vanochengeta avo vanoita mabasa akanaka.”"
  7,197,“Uye avo vamunodaidza kunze kwaAllah havakwanisi kukubatsirai kana kuzvibatsira pachavo.”
  7,198,"“Uye kana mukavadaidzira kuchokwadi havanzwi, uye unovaona vakakutarisa asi havaoni.”"
  7,199,"Iva unoratidza ruregerero, uye kurudzira zvakanaka, uye furatira avo vasingazivi (usavaranga)"
  7,200,"Uye kana kuzevezera kwakashata kwauya kwauri kubva kuna Dhiyabhorosi, tsvaga chengetedzo kubva kuna Allah. Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vanonzwa zvese, vanoziva zvose"
  7,201,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotya Allah, kana zvakaipa zvikauya kwavari kubva kuna Dhiyabhorosi, vanorangarira (Allah), uye vanobva vaona (chokwadi)"
  7,202,"Uye madzikoma avo (vanaDhiyabhorosi) vanovawedzera kutadza, zvakare havaregeri"
  7,203,"Uye ukasavaunzira chishamiso vanoti: “Sei usina kutiunzira chishamiso?” Iti: “Zvirokwazvo, ndinongotevera chete izvo zvakadzikiswa kwandiri kubva kunaTenzi vangu. Iri (Qur’aan) ndihwo humboo kubva kuna Tenzi venyu, nekutungamirwa uye tsitsi kuvanhu vanotenda.”"
  7,204,"Uye kana Qur’aan richiverengwa ivai munoriteerera, uye monyarara kuti pamwe mungaratidzwe tsitsi (naAllah)"
  7,205,"Uye rangarira Tenzi vako pachezvako uchizvininipisa nekutya, uye neizwi riripasi mangwanani nemanheru, uye usave umwe veavo vasina hanya"
  7,206,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vana Tenzi vako (ngirozi) havazvitutumadze mukuvanamata, asi vanovarumbidza uye vanovapfugamira"